        <p class="relative text-2xl  z-20 text-center p-6 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
        Food systems, climate systems, economic systems—most are too large to see clearly or feel agency within.
      </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Regeneration happens at human scale.</h3>
        <p class="relative text-2xl z-20 text-center p-6 flex flex-col justify-center h-full">
